name: Grassetto Symbols Lampshade 45cm - Indigo Blue/Ochre Yellow
description: This bold range focuses on pattern. Its hieroglyph-style design is screen printed onto a natural tussar silk base. This indigo pattern is gathered by hand to form a pleated appearance and framed by the contrasting warmth of the ochre trim. The silk is hand stitched onto its metal frame and lined with cotton. This is the larger of two sizes, which will make a real statement with an oversized lamp base.
